p= `Hi admin, ${buyer.firstName || ''} ${buyer.lastName || ''} just made a purchase below are the order details`
h3 Order Details
table(border=1)
    tr
        th Order Number
        td #{order.orderNumber}
    tr
        th Total Product
        td #{order.totalProduct}
    tr
        th Total Quantities
        td #{order.totalQuantities}
    tr
        th Product Details
        td
            table(border=0)
                thead
                tr
                    th Product Name
                    th Quantity
                    th Unit Price
                    th Unit Subtotal
                tbody
                  each item in cart
                    td= item.product.name
                    td= item.quantity
                    td= item.unitPrice
                    td= item.subTotal

    tr
        th Subtotal
        td #{order.subTotal}

h4 Take Action
p Your action is needed for this order<br/> APPROVE : <a href="#{process.env.APP_URL}/order/update-approval-status/#{order.token}/#{admin._id}/approved"> #{process.env.APP_URL}/order/update-approval-status/#{order.token}/#{admin._id}/approved</a><br/>
<strong>Or</strong>
p DECLINE: <a href="#{process.env.APP_URL}/order/update-approval-status/#{order.token}/#{admin._id}/declined"> #{process.env.APP_URL}/order/update-approval-status/#{order.token}/#{admin._id}/declined</a>
